Title: Flatmates Bill
Description: An app that gets amount of bill as input for particular month(period)
and the each of the flatmates have to pay bill according to the number of days they
stayed in the house. it also generated pdf of names for paying amount of each flatmate.

Objects;

1. Bill:
        amount
        period
2. flatmate:
        name
        days_in_house
        pays(bill)
3. pdfReport:
        filename
        generate(flatmate1,flatmate2,bill)